snippet.title: NES Longplay [357] 1991 Du Ma Racing (Unlicensed)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by JagOfTroy

Another... horse racing game.
At least this one was a bit more entertaining but still has no official end.
The first part is an action scene where you race a horse against an opponent.
The second part you just bet on horses as per usual. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
